Easy enough but not so easy as to take away the mystery. Great story line and I like how you did the HO puzzles. This part of the game can usually be pretty boring but I'm actually enjoying them. Kudos and thanks for all your hard work!!

I love all their names expecially the wolf 104 of my expertise I just hope that they keep coming over more games like this the graphics were awesome the puzzles were hard but not too hard it was just an all-around fun game

This game has a glitch in it and it needs an update. Half way through the game the saddle disappears from your inventory and you cannot go any further in the game. I contacted the makers a few weeks ago and still haven't received a response. I also saw in other forums that this problem is not new. I wish I had read up on the game before purchasing. I am definitely going to stop buying these games sight unseen because they are offered at a discounted rate. The catch is you have to buy them outrite. I buy  2 to 3 games at a time because they are offered on weekly sales, but when you try to play the games they have problems. Buyer beware.....don't waste your money.
